  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a trial of treatment with tablets containing magnesium for leg cramps in pregnancy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Healthy pregnant women between 18 and 36 weeks of pregnancy suffering from leg cramps at
      least twice a week were treated with magnesium tablets or placebo for two weeks, 120 mg x 3
      daily.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
