  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant women with recurrent leg cramps (at least twice a week).

          -  No disease according to helath certificate. Written participation consent must be
             signed.

          -  Linguistic ability demanded: Norwegian as the first language. Gestation length more
             than 17 weeks, less than 36 weeks.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Twin pregnancy.

          -  Oedema.

          -  Pre-eclampsia.

          -  Magnesium supplementation beyond the trial treatment.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
